
  Spoink    Psychic Type Pokémon

  SPOINK bounces around on its 
  tail.  The shock of its bouncing 
  makes its heart pump.  As a result, 
  Spoink cannot afford to 
  stop bouncing - if it stops, 
  its heart will stop. 
	Evolution Chain
      Spoink ► Grumpig

